movie_name: Bad Faith: Christian Nationalism's Unholy War on Democracy
short_description: Exposes how Christian Nationalism has become the most powerful anti-democratic force in America. Leaders join forces to defend our country from this march to fascism, but American citizens seem unaware of the threat.
